headline: Henry Schein Opens Customer Emergency Support Hotline in Response to California Fires
summary: MELVILLE, N.Y., January 09, 2025--Henry Schein, Inc. (Nasdaq: HSIC) reminds its customers throughout California that the Henry Schein Customer Emergency Support Hotline is open for dental and medical professionals who may experience operational, logistical, or financial issues as a result of damage caused by the ongoing fires.
